<p>
    
    
       
      
   
        
        <p>Effective Date: [3-08-2023]</p>

        <p>At Coding Hub, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect the information gathered when you use our Student Management web application (referred to as "App"). By accessing or using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with the practices described herein, please refrain from using the App.</p>

        <h2>1. Information Collected:</h2>
